This project is a MOD for "Star Fox 64: Recompiled". It contains NO Nintendo
assets, ROM data, or copyrighted game content. A legally obtained copy of the
original game is required by the recompilation to play. Star Fox 64 is a
trademark of Nintendo. This project is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Nintendo.

